name: Reggi Tirver
content:
Reggi Tirver was a male Gran who worked as a junk dealer in Nym's Base on Lok in 1 ABY.
Reggi Tirver appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
